Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}気づいていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:25.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}恵まれたまわりに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.43,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甘えてたあの頃さ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.73,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}目の前には
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いつも　沢山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:35.68,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見守る人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.36,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仲間たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.31,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}支え合った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.41,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}抜け出せない
