Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.74,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}風を入れろ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:51.93,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}チームよ、目を覚ませ!
