Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:39.12,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}谁也未曾见过的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.88,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}容纳着风!
