Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大好きだ　ずっと　大好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}声の限り叫ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.19,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大好きだ　君が　大好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.23,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}息が苦しくなるよ
