Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:28.91,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつかの願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.37,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}土の中で眠って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:42.63,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}約束の時刻に 希望の根が出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:46.64,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}二人が出会った頃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.68,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢など まだだめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:55.61,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どれくらい時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:01.07,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花は咲くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:06.37,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:10.83,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.42,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:21.05,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:24.51,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:29.14,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:34.27,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.61,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:28.91,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何时的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.37,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:42.63,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在约定好的时间 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:46.64,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}当两人相遇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.68,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:55.61,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要过多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:01.07,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才会绽放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:06.37,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把这颗眼泪献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:10.83,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能够更加闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.42,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会从一直看着你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:21.05,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:24.51,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:29.14,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:34.27,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是轻轻抚慰空虚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.61,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来吧 我将成为雨
